      <div class="up-cell spot"><div class="up-num"><span class="cnt" data-to="100">100</span><span>%</span></div><div class="up-lbl">Job success score · Top Rated Plus</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="up-note fu fd2">
      <div class="up-note-ic">✓</div>
      <p><strong>Why this matters for AI work:</strong> These numbers represent 4 years of shipping production software on deadline, communicating clearly under pressure, and delivering exactly what was scoped. That delivery discipline is what separates AI systems that get built, deployed, and used — from AI demos that never leave staging.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
